Name: sally
Version: 0.1.0
Summary: A command line tool to check the status of repositories in all subdirectories
Home-page: https://github.com/luciopaiva/sally
Author: Lucio Paiva
Author-email: luciopaiva@gmail.com
License: MIT
Description: Sally
        =====
        
        Checks the status of all repositories in subdirectories.
        
        Sally goes into every subdirectory to see if there's a git and/or a mercurial repo. In case there is one (there may be
        both!), sally runs :code:`git/hg status` to see if there's any uncommited changes.
        
Keywords: version control git mercurial
